"```sql\nSELECT p.FavoriteCount\nFROM comments c\nJOIN posts p ON c.PostId = p.Id\nWHERE c.UserId = 3025 AND c.CreationDate = '2014-04-23 20:29:39.0';\n```\n\nThis SQL query selects the `FavoriteCount` of the post that received a comment from user number 3025 at the specified date and time. It joins the `comments` table with the `posts` table using the `PostId` foreign key relationship to find the relevant post."